title: Thomas Brown // 35
description:
In Fall 2016, a high school senior doesn't come home by curfew and his mom reports him missing. The small Texas town immediately starts looking for him, and within a few hours, they find his car abandoned on a dirt road. The contents of his car raise more questions than answers as people start to believe something really bad happened to him. This is the case of Thomas Brown.
